The postmaster has received a transit commission for a complete route survey of Shadowmere. The blighted realm has no current documentation in Midgaard's civic reference archive, which creates difficulties for any courier or recovery team operating in the area. Map every accessible section and return with a complete navigation record so the route can be formally documented.
Your Shadowmere survey has been filed in Midgaard's civic archive. The postmaster has marked the transit commission fulfilled and forwarded the route record to the dispatch office for incorporation into regional navigation documentation.
